  <brief_title>Helicobacter Pylori Eradication and Irritable Bowel Syndrome: A Prospective Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Helicobacter Pylori Eradication on Symptoms and Quality of Life of Irritable Bowel Syndrome: A Prospective Study</official_title>
